-- C  R U  D Operations:- 
C    -> Create or new information store in the database table.

Create  or CREATE or CrEate or create ( command )

R   -> Read or retrive or fetch
Select  ( command )

U  -> Update or edit information which have already store in the database table
Update  ( command ) 

D  -> Delete information from the database table

Delete  ( command )
